{"url":"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/staff/post-4900","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"ja\">\n<head>\n<title>&#x1f411;牧歌の里&#x1f490;で動物たちと友達になれた日 | アルプ薬局 ブログ</title>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1\">\n\n<!-- All in One SEO Pack 2.3.12 by Michael Torbert of Semper Fi Web Design[40,94] -->\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/staff/post-4900\" />\n<!-- /all in one seo pack -->\n<link rel='dns-prefetch' href='//ajax.googleapis.com' />\n<link rel='dns-prefetch' href='//s.w.org' />\n<link rel='stylesheet' id='style-css'  href='https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/style.css?ver=4.7.3' type='text/css' media='all' />\n<script type='text/javascript' src='http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js?ver=4.7.3'></script>\n<link rel='shortlink' href='https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/?p=4900' />\n\n<link rel=\"pingback\" href=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/xmlrpc.php\">\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"//fonts.googleapis.com/earlyaccess/notosansjapanese.css\">\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/earlyaccess/mplus1p.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" />\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/js/touch.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/js/tabmenu.js\"></script>\n<link rel=\"apple-touch-icon-precomposed\" href=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/img/webclip.png\" />\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/img/alp.ico\">\n<!--[if lt IE 9]>\n<script src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/js/respond.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/js/html5.js\"></script>\n<![endif]-->\n\n</head>\n\n<body>\n\t\n<!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->\n<script async src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-Y3YBPRXKL3\"></script>\n<script>\n  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];\n  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}\n  gtag('js', new Date());\n\n  gtag('config', 'G-Y3YBPRXKL3');\n</script>\n<div id=\"wrapper\">\n\n<header id=\"site-header\" role=\"banner\">\n\t\n\n<div class=\"site-title\"><h1><a href=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp\" rel=\"home\"><img src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/img/logo.png\" width=\"180\"  alt=\"アルプ薬局\"></a></h1></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"blog-title\"><h2>スタッフブログ</h2></div>\n<div class=\"blog-title2\"><p>アルプスタッフがつぶやく、日々の徒然日記</p></div><div class=\"blog-title-img\"><img src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/img/alp-blog-01.jpg\"></div>\n\n\n\n\n</header>\n\n<div id=\"content\">   \n\n\t<div class=\"post\"> \n<div class=\"post-single\">\n\t\t\n\t\t<div id=\"breadcrumb\">\n        <span class=\"bread\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://data-vocabulary.org/Breadcrumb\"><a href=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/\" itemprop=\"url\"><span itemprop=\"title\">TOP</span> </a></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<span class=\"bread\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://data-vocabulary.org/Breadcrumb\"> <a href=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/category/staff\" itemprop=\"url\"><span itemprop=\"title\">スタッフブログ</span></a></span>\t\t</div>\n\n\n<article itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Article\" role=\"main\">\n\n<header>\n<h1 itemprop=\"headline\">&#x1f411;牧歌の里&#x1f490;で動物たちと友達になれた日</h1>\n<div class=\"align-right\"><p><i class=\"fa fa-calendar\"></i> <time itemprop=\"datePublished\" datetime=\"2025-12-05T00:00:43+00:00\">2025/12/05</time></p></div>\n</header>\n\n\n<div itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">岐阜県にある<strong><span style=\"color: #008000\">「牧歌の里」</span></strong>へ行ってきました～☘️</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">広い<strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff\">青空</span></strong>と<span style=\"color: #008000\"><strong>草原</strong></span>に囲まれた、</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">まさに<span style=\"color: #ff9900\"><strong>癒しの楽園✨</strong></span>のような場所でした☀️&#x1f44f;</span></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-4917\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/ec63b0efa3782db84377d0e71181fcad-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"580\" height=\"387\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/ec63b0efa3782db84377d0e71181fcad-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/ec63b0efa3782db84377d0e71181fcad-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/ec63b0efa3782db84377d0e71181fcad-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/ec63b0efa3782db84377d0e71181fcad.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> &#x1f40f;<strong>羊に出会えた感動<br />\n</strong></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">ふわふわの<strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff\">「ひつじ」</span></strong>たちが集まってきてくれました&#x1f411;&#x1f495;</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">ふわふわの毛に<strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">まんまるの目が</span></strong>本当に<strong><span style=\"color: #ff00ff\">可愛かったです&#x1f60a;&#x1f495;</span></strong></span></p>\n<p><strong>「</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><strong><span style=\"color: #993300\">餌やり体験」</span></strong>もできたので、</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600\">にんじん</span></strong>を手にしてゆっくり近づいてみると、<br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">羊たちが優しく<span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>ポリポリ</strong></span>と食べてくれました✨&#x1f60a;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br />\n<img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-4902\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/02-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"580\" height=\"435\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/02-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/02-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/02-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/02.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /><br />\n</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#x1f40e;<strong>人生初の乗馬体験</strong><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">そのあとは、ずっと楽しみにしていた<span style=\"color: #993300\">「</span></span><span style=\"color: #993300\"><b>乗馬体験」</b></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">へ&#x1f40e;</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">人生で<strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600\">初めての乗馬</span></strong>だったので、最初は<strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff\">ちょっと緊張&#x1f4a6;</span></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">でも案内された馬は<span style=\"color: #ff9900\"><strong>女の子の馬</strong></span>で、とても落ち着いた性格でした&#x1f338;&#x1f490;</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">なんと、名前とプロフィールが載った「</span><b>名刺」</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">まであって、思わず<span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><strong>笑顔</strong></span>&#x1f60a;に</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff99cc\">（名刺をもらう瞬間が可愛すぎて忘れられない…！）</span></strong><br />\n<img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-4907\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/f4205a7fc8c643dc3b86b8c5b1e653d7-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"580\" height=\"387\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/f4205a7fc8c643dc3b86b8c5b1e653d7-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/f4205a7fc8c643dc3b86b8c5b1e653d7-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/f4205a7fc8c643dc3b86b8c5b1e653d7-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/f4205a7fc8c643dc3b86b8c5b1e653d7.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /><br />\n</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><strong>&#x1f4ab;「動物」</strong>と友達になれる幸せ✨<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><strong><span style=\"color: #008000\">牧歌の里</span></strong>での時間は、ただ遊んだだけじゃなくて、</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><strong>「動物と心が通うって、こんなに嬉しいんだ」</strong></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">と感じられた、とても大切な一日でした&#x1f495;&#x1f642;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff6600\"><strong>「また絶対行きたい～！」</strong></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">次はもっともっと、いろんな動物と<span style=\"color: #ff00ff\"><strong>友達</strong></span>になりたいな</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">〜✨&#x1f601;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-4905\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/cfa8b3e1fa50b36f2dba85e72feba21e-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"580\" height=\"435\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/cfa8b3e1fa50b36f2dba85e72feba21e-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/cfa8b3e1fa50b36f2dba85e72feba21e-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/cfa8b3e1fa50b36f2dba85e72feba21e-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/cfa8b3e1fa50b36f2dba85e72feba21e.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>アルプトラベル　F</p>\n<div class=\"blog-alp-logo\"><img src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/img/alp-logo.jpg\" width=\"130\" alt=\"アルプ薬局\"></div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"ninja_onebutton\">\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n//<![CDATA[\n(function(d){\nif(typeof(window.NINJA_CO_JP_ONETAG_BUTTON_2e525997ea6182d4250a7da41cf